name: Cowshed at my grandmother's house
description:
This sketch illustrates how Indonesians in rural areas raise cows, one farmer on average only has one to four cows, so the size of the cage is small.

Size 42 x 29,7 cm, Size 42 x 29,7 cm, Produced july 29 2014, Dimensions 2227 x 1560
